event: message_saved
data: {"messageId":"-91a5Fjj6PpLXV87on_d2","role":"user","content":"Analyze the OpenAgentic GitHub repository and CI/CD pipeline. Execute ALL steps:\n\n1. Use get_user to check which GitHub account is authenticated\n\n2. Use list_repos to find OpenAgentic-related repositories\n\n3. Use search_repos to search for 'openagentic' or 'agentic' repositories\n\n4. If you find the main repo, use list_branches to show all branches\n\n5. Use list_workflows to check CI/CD pipelines configured\n\n6. Use get_workflow_runs to check recent CI/CD run results\n\n7. Use list_commits to show the last 10 commits on the main branch\n\n8. Use list_issues to check open issues\n\n9. Use list_pull_requests to check open PRs\n\nPresent findings as:\n- Repository overview (branches, recent activity)\n- CI/CD pipeline status (passing/failing, last run time)\n- Open issues and PRs summary\n- Security posture (any security-related issues or workflows)\n\nEven if GitHub auth isn't configured, attempt ALL calls and report what works.","timestamp":"2026-02-20T22:03:19.789Z","source":"database","confirmed":true}

