ub","url":"https://github.com/irfanfadhullah/Awesome-Agentic-Workflow","snippet":"A curated collection ofGitHubrepositories focused on agentic workflows, autonomous agents, multi-agent systems, and AI workflow automation. Thisrepositoryserves as a comprehensive resource hub containing summarized documentation from projects related to intelligent agent frameworks and automated workflow orchestration."},{"title":"With Agentic Workflows, GitHub wants to help automate repo maintenance","url":"https://tessl.io/blog/with-agentic-workflows-github-wants-to-help-automate-repo-maintenance/","snippet":"\"The use ofGitHubAgentic Workflows makes entirely new categories ofrepositoryautomation and software engineering possible, in a way that fits naturally with how developer teams already work onGitHub,\"GitHubwrote in a blog post. One exampleGitHubprovides is a daily issues report workflow."},{"title":"Agentic Workflows - GitHub Next","url":"https://githubnext.com/projects/agentic-workflows/","snippet":"Software collaboration keeps evolving. With Continuous AI,GitHubNext are exploring how LLMs can help teams with documentation, quality, triage, and more. Agentic Workflows is a follow‑up exploration: a research demonstrator focused on expressing repository‑level behaviors in natural language and running them onGitHub."},{"title":"GitHub Agentic Workflows Bring AI Agents to Actions - Ken Muse","url":"https://www.kenmuse.com/blog/github-agentic-workflows-bring-ai-agents-to-actions/","snippet":"ExploreGitHub'snew Agentic Workflows -- AI coding agents inGitHubActions with defense-in-depth security and natural language automation."},{"title":"Building and Running Agentic Workflows: A New Era of Automation on GitHub","url":"https://medium.com/@mvpkenlin/building-and-running-agentic-workflows-a-new-era-of-automation-on-github-99b70916cc13","snippet":"Automation onGitHubis evolving fast, and one of the most exciting shifts is the rise of agentic workflows — a model where AI agents execute